attributes.body:
Wyld Sours are a new adventure on the Wyld journey. Whether enjoyed with a group of your favorite people or at the peak ofyour expedition, our new line of flavors offer a burst of refreshment and relief with every serving. Not too sweet, and not too tart, Wyld Sours offer an experience for everyone.


Our Sour Cherry gummies offer a mellow + carefree experience that packs a tart punch.


It's a little like a hammock for your inner thoughts. Enjoy!


100mg THC per container, 10mg THC per gummy.


Contains: Coconut

attributes.name: Strawberry 20:1 CBD + Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 200:10mg
attributes.body:
Our Strawberry 20:1 CBD:THC gummies are made with real fruit, a Hybrid terpene blend, and enhanced with cannabis-derived CBD oil. Perfect for relaxing your body while keeping your mind sharp and alert. They are the go-to gummy if you are looking to decompress or take the edge off.


It’s a little like a spa treatment for your body and soul. Enjoy!


200mg CBD:10mg THC per package, 20mg CBD:1mg THC per gummy.


Contains: Coconut

attributes.name: Raspberry Sativa Enhanced Gummies 100mg
attributes.body:
Our Raspberry Sativa gummies are made with real fruit and enhanced with botanical terpenes that may assist in creating euphoric and energizing experiences. Ideal for keeping you focused on the task at hand, refining your creative endeavors, or even better, getting you out on your next expedition!


It's a little like surfing the clouds on a surfboard made of pure energy. Enjoy!


100mg THC per package, 10mg THC per gummy.


Contains: Coconut

attributes.name: Peach 2:1 CBD + Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 100:50mg
attributes.body:
New to edibles? Our Peach 2:1 CBD:THC gummies are made with more CBD than THC, making them a great option for easing into edibles. They are made with real fruit and enhanced with a balanced Hybrid terpene profile that may assist in creating a sense of ease and overall well being.


It’s a little like a vacation for your body. Enjoy!


100mg CBD:50mg THC per package, 10mg CBD:5mg THC per gummy.


Contains: Coconut

attributes.name: Pear 1:1 CBG + Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 100mg
attributes.body:
The restorative effects of CBG in combination with THC, alongside the terpenes found in Hybrid strains may provide greater rejuvenation than THC alone. This combination may be particularly useful when looking for balance.


It's a little like a bubble bath for your brain. Enjoy!


100mg THC:100mg CBG per container, 10mg THC:10mg CBG per gummy.

attributes.name: Marionberry Indica Enhanced Gummies 100mg
attributes.body:
Our Marionberry gummies are made with real fruit and an Indica enhanced botanical terpene blend, making them a great addition to the end of any long day. Whether eaten around a campfire, or in the comfort of your own home, these gummies are great for unwinding.


It’s a little like the soft furry slippers for your mind. Enjoy!


100mg THC per package, 10mg THC per gummy.

attributes.name: Elderberry 2:1 CBN + Indica Enhanced Gummies 100mg:50mg
attributes.body:

It’s a little like watching sheep count you. Enjoy!


100mg THC:50mg CBN per container, 10mg THC:5mg CBN per gummy.

attributes.name: Huckleberry Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 100mg

attributes.name: Pomegranate 1:1 CBD + Hybrid Enhanced Gummies 100:100mg
attributes.body:

They are a great compliment to any adventure by providing a balanced and enjoyable high for both mind and body using a Hybrid terpene blend. If you are new or sensitive to edibles, the Pomegranate gummies are an excellent place to start. Have some before getting into your yoga routine, or climbing to the highest peak.

attributes.name: Twax Infused Pre-roll 1.25g | Lemon Haze
attributes.body:
Twax by The Clear™ is an infused pre-rolled joint for the experienced cannabis consumer. We grind full flower to the perfect consistency for the perfect burn. Then, our proprietary infusion process pumps up the potency for the perfect punch, every time. It provides the potency you need, with the smoothness and burnability you expect.


The TWAX Pre-roll is perfect for consumers that wants to add a twist of flavor to their smoke. Lemon Haze is loud, tangy, and delicious. The sweet, sour notes burst onto the tongue immediately upon inhale and the impact of tasty lemon zest persists through exhale while lingering on the tongue. 


Each pre-roll contains dye-free, unbleached papers, 1.25 grams of premium bud, 200mg of AAA Grade flavored distillate and naturally derived plant terpenes.

attributes.name: TWAX Mini Infused Pre-rolls 3.5g [7 pack] | Banana Cream
attributes.body:
TWAX minis are the perfect small flavorful enhancements to your day or night. These infused mini pre-rolls pack a punch and are rolled with dye-free papers for a smooth burn. Each joint contains .5 grams of full flower that is paired with AAA-grade distillate and plant-derived terpenes.


Banana Cream is impressively rich, while maintaining an elegant balance of banana and creaminess. Its highly nostalgic banana flavor finishes with a pleasantly smooth cream note. 


Seven minis per tin, ideal for when you’re on the go with a total of 3.5 grams of premium-infused flower.

attributes.name: Sativa Chocolate Taffy Chews | 100mg
attributes.body:
Uplifting and inspired. These sativa dominant THC infused, deliciously rich chocolate taffy chews contain 10mg in each piece with ten pieces per package. Multi-award winning flavor and effect.

Each batch of high grade cannabis oil used to make Cheeba Chews™ is tested at three critical stages…The Flower, The Oil, The Edible…to ensure each individual chew is consistently infused.

Gluten, Peanut Free.

attributes.name: Hybrid Caramel Chews | 100mg
attributes.body:
A balanced blend. Buttery smooth, low calorie, creamy caramel with 10mg of fast acting THC in each bite sized chew. 100mg of high grade THC in each package.

Each batch of high grade cannabis oil used to make Cheeba Chews™ is tested at three critical stages…The Flower, The Oil, The Edible…to ensure each individual chew is consistently infused.

Gluten, Peanut Free.

attributes.name: Indica Strawberry Fruit Chews | 100mg
attributes.body:
As one of the cannabis industry’s best tasting edibles, each award winning sweet strawberry flavored fruit taffy chew is infused with 10mg of high-grade indica dominant THC oil. Each package we produce is tested at three levels: The flower, the oil, and the edible, to ensure consistency.

Dairy, Gluten, Peanut Free.
